PortSystem          1.0
PortGroup           cmake 1.0

name                Vc
version             0.7.4
categories          devel
license             LGPL
maintainers         gmail.com:mschamschula openmaintainer
description         Vc is a free software library to ease explicit vectorization of \
                    C++ code.
long_description    ${description} It has an intuitive API and provides portability \
                    between different compilers and compiler versions as well as \
                    portability between different vector instruction sets.
platforms           darwin
homepage            http://code.compeng.uni-frankfurt.de/projects/vc
master_sites        http://code.compeng.uni-frankfurt.de/attachments/download/183/

